===Noun===
'''hyperbola''' (''plural'' '''hyperbolas''' ''or'' '''hyperbolae''')
{{wikipedia}}
#(''mathematics'') A [[conic section]] formed by the [[intersection]] of a [[cone]] with a [[plane]] that intersects the [[base]] of the cone and is not [[tangent]] to the cone.

